title: Week 4 Preview, WWE's Jim Ross on Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: Week 4 Preview, WWE's Jim Ross on Baker Mayfield
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the biggest matchups from the NFL slate this weekend including Jets vs. Jaguars & Ravens vs. Steelers (11:17). They also dive into some of the challenges defensive coordinators face going up against the evolving offenses in the NFL (1:58). DJ & Bucky then welcome back WWE Hall of Fame inductee Jim Ross to reveal what he said to his friend, Baker Mayfield, this past weekend following the rookie's first win (25:33). The guys also pick the top 10 college football games of the weekend (38:55).
